Package entities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Comment
    The Comment class keeps track of the commenterUsername, timeCommented and text.
    Crop
    The Crop class keeps track of the cropName, minYield, maxYield, salePrice, cost, timeToHarvest and xp.
    GiftThread
    The GiftThread class keeps track of the senderUsername, receiverUsername, timePosted and cropName of a gift thread.
    Plot
    The Plot class keeps track of the plotId, ownerUsername timeCropPlanted, remainingPercentage, cropName and originalYield of a plot.
    PostThread
    The PostThread class keeps track of the senderUsername, receiverUsername, timePosted and text of a post thread.
    Reaction
    The Reaction class keeps track of a reaction's reactorUsername, timeReacted and reactionType (like or dislike).
    Thread
    The Thread class keeps track of the senderUsername, receiverUsername and timePosted of a thread
    User
    The User class keeps track of the username, fullName, rank, xp and gold of a user.
